<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Jesus must have been extremely devastated after hearing about John's death at the hands of Herod but that doesn't give Him any excuse to not be compassionate to others. Anxiety, stress, and grief is no excuse to treat others with anything short of compassion.</p></body></html>